svt_axi_tlm_generic_payload_sequencer Class Reference

Inheritance diagram for class svt_axi_tlm_generic_payload_sequencer:

List of all members.

Detailed Description

This class is UVM Sequencer that provides stimulus for the svt_axi_master_sequencer class. The svt_axi_master_agent class is responsible for connecting this sequencer to the svt_axi_master_sequencer if the agent is configured as UVM_ACTIVE.
